    "Machine learning techniques provide computers with the ability to learn from data and further anticipate the future.",
    "Jordan and Mitchell (2015) claim that within AI, ML has become a viable option for creating useful tools to address a variety of problems.",
    "For example, forecasting student enrollment, teacher and student performance evaluation, forecasting student grade point average, and other aspects of education management use popular soft computing techniques including fuzzy logic, neural networks, and genetic algorithms (Khan et al., 2018).",
